Course Description
- discrete-event dynamic systems
-  simulation-based methods

 --------------- 课程目标 --------------- 
• develop simulation models and conduct simulation studies.
• Become familiar with the organization of simulation languages. 使用Arena
• Review statistical aspects including input analysis, random variate generation, output analysis, and variance reduction techniques.

 --------------- Syllabus --------------- 
• 2个midterms和1个final。考题是多选题或者是非题.
• 11个Homework. 有bonus questions
• 作业晚交的话: 10% * 晚的天数，但是不能晚超过3天
• Project可以从几个several theory中选择，可以in small groups.
 
